    <h1>Welcome to Helpables Aid App</h1>
    <p><strong>A platform where kindness meets action!</strong></p>
    <p>Discover aid requests from people in need and lend a helping hand effortlessly. Whether it's food, shelter, or essentials, you can make a real difference in someone's life. Browse verified requests, offer assistance, and be a hero in your community.</p>

    <h2>About Helpables</h2>
    <p>Helpables Aid App is a platform designed to connect compassionate individuals with those in need. Whether you’re looking to make a difference in your community or find people who need urgent assistance, this app makes it easy to browse, filter, and search for aid requests near you.</p>

    <h2>Key Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Easy Sign-Up & Login</strong> – Register with your email or log in using Google for a seamless experience.</li>
        <li><strong>Discover Aid Requests</strong> – Explore requests from different areas and find people in need of help.</li>
        <li><strong>Smart Filtering & Search</strong> – Filter requests by category or location to find relevant cases quickly.</li>
        <li><strong>Detailed Request Information</strong> – View the title, description, location, categories, subcategories, and images of each aid request.</li>
        <li><strong>Engaging Visuals</strong> – Browse images uploaded by requesters to better understand their needs.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Who It's For</h2>
    <p>Helpables Aid App is built for volunteers, donors, and anyone with a helping heart. The intuitive interface ensures you can find aid requests effortlessly, making it easier to contribute and support those who need it most.</p>

    <h2>Get Involved</h2>
    <p>Join Helpables Aid App today and start making a difference!</p>

    <h3>Contact</h3>
